to help you decipher the map?

06:12.097 --> 06:13.107
Yes.

06:13.139 --> 06:15.665
Exactly, that's awesome.
Please, decipher the map.

06:15.950 --> 06:16.976
The only thing is,

06:17.008 --> 06:19.613
