08:07.868 --> 08:09.813
Hey, hey, guys.
Over here.

08:13.548 --> 08:15.491
Check this out,
we totally got something.

08:15.668 --> 08:17.294
- Mr. M.?
- Okay.

08:17.455 --> 08:18.725
I don't think this is "Route 44"

