psychobabble crap he learned in college.

13:43.680 --> 13:45.180
- Wanna hear something funny?
- No.

13:45.846 --> 13:48.487
When I was a kid, guess what I
wanted to be.

13:48.762 --> 13:50.193
A shrink like my old man.

13:51.382 --> 13:52.382
Maybe you will.

13:53.683 --> 13:55.956
Yeah, or maybe I won't
have to work at all.

13:57.298 --> 14:00.055
Anyway, next time you're in session,
tell him I said hi.

14:00.104 --> 14:02.141
Troy, pull over. Pull over.

14:08.278 --> 14:11.404
It's not a "Z." It's a "2."

14:11.674 --> 14:13.095
The 200.

14:13.363 --> 14:15.363
That means we take the next left...

