14:38.441 --> 14:39.641
Mr. Connelly.

14:39.931 --> 14:41.952
Karen, you didn't need to come in today.

14:41.984 --> 14:44.369
I know, I just...
I didn't want to be alone.

14:44.432 --> 14:47.800
Well... I'm glad you're here. Any calls?

14:47.917 --> 14:48.917
Uh, the police.

14:48.975 --> 14:50.459
Detectives keep calling.

14:51.224 --> 14:52.992
- Anybody else?
- Nope, that's it.

14:53.039 --> 14:54.041
Okay.

14:54.088 --> 14:55.304
- Thanks.
- bye.

14:56.590 --> 14:59.472
- We are. We're facing north, right?
- Right.

15:00.013 --> 15:01.618
There's the reservoir.

15:02.590 --> 15:06.079
Supposed to be a barbeque over there?

15:06.576 --> 15:09.171
Barbeque, that doesn't make any sense.

15:11.629 --> 15:13.102
How old do you think she is?

15:14.811 --> 15:16.663
I don't know, 34 maybe.

15:17.844 --> 15:18.981
